OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782146887
OL,3,CSouth East Water asks thousands of
OL,4,Ccustomers not to use hosepipes amid
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FSouth East Water is urging people not
OL,8,Fto use their hosepipes during the
OL,9,Fongoing heatwave.
OL,11,FThe company which supplies water to
OL,12,Fhomes and businesses in Kent, Sussex,
OL,13,FSurrey, Hampshire and Berkshire said
OL,14,Fthat demand is higher due to the hot
OL,15,Fweather and is asking customers to
OL,16,Fonly use water for "essential
OL,17,Fpurposes."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
