OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782146887
OL,3,CSouth East Water asks thousands of
OL,4,Ccustomers not to use hosepipes amid
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FPeople are being warned to stop using
OL,8,Fhoses, including for refilling
OL,9,Fpaddling pools, hot tubs and jet
OL,10,Fwashing, and to only use water for
OL,11,Fwashing, drinking and cooking.
OL,13,FA South East Water spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"The total amount of water treated and
OL,15,Fput into South East Water's network
OL,16,Fwas 644 million litres, that's 56
OL,17,Fmillion litres more than the daily
OL,18,Faverage for June (588 million litres).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
