OL,3,CSouth East Water asks thousands of
OL,4,Ccustomers not to use hosepipes amid
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,F"It's anticipated that this figure
OL,8,Fwill rise further with hotter weather
OL,9,Fforecast for later this week."
OL,11,FMore follows.
